			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Right Whales Are Losing the Right Genes</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Losing young is sad, but for small inbred populations it can sometimes be a good thing—in the long run.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/bas-den-hond/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Bas den Hond</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						January 31, 2024 | 750 words, about 3 minutes					</aside>
