						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0ARight Whales Are Losing the Right Genes%0D%0ALosing young is sad, but for small inbred populations it can sometimes be a good thing—in the long run.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/right-whales-are-losing-the-right-genes/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



